    "button[aria-label='Speichern']",
    "button[aria-label='Enregistrer']"
  ],
  "_comment_save_button": "Priority: stable class/ID first (locale-independent), structural fallback, locale-specific aria-labels LAST. YtSaveButtonPlaceholderHost is YouTube's Polymer component class — stable across locales.",
